Let's pray.

740
00:44:10.400 --> 00:44:16.400
Lord, we thank you so much that you are God of mercy and steadfast love.

741
00:44:16.400 --> 00:44:25.400
Lord, we thank you that you are God who receives us in our brokenness, makes us new.

742
00:44:25.400 --> 00:44:32.400
We thank you that you invite us to weep before you, that you hear the sound of our weeping.

743
00:44:32.400 --> 00:44:39.400
So Lord, I pray that you would help us to bring our tears to you but also to place our trust in you.

744
00:44:39.400 --> 00:44:45.400
And as we do so, Lord, we pray that your beauty would be displayed even through our brokenness.

745
00:44:45.400 --> 00:44:48.400
In Jesus' name, amen.

